  "status": "success",
  "answer": "The process for the Conversion of a Foreign Driver's License to a Philippine Driver's License is as follows:\n\n### **Who May Avail**\n1. Must be physically and mentally fit to operate a motor vehicle.\n2. Must be able to read and write in English, Filipino, and/or any major dialect.\n3. Must hold a valid foreign driver's license. (If the foreign license is expired, the applicant must pass the Theoretical Examination and Practical Driving Test).\n4. Must have no unsettled traffic violations.\n5. Must have a valid visa for at least 120 days upon the date of arrival.\n6. Applicants from countries operating right-hand drive vehicles must pass a practical examination.\n\n### **Documentary Requirements**\n- **APL Form:** Duly accomplished Application for Permits and Licenses Form.\n- **Medical Certificate:** Electronically transmitted medical certificate from an LTO-accredited clinic (plus 1 photocopy).\n- **Foreign Driver's License:** Original and 1 photocopy. If not in English, an original official English translation is required.\n- **Passport and Visa:** Original and 1 photocopy of the valid passport (showing the first page, visa page, and latest date of entry).\n- **TIN:** Taxpayer Identification Number (if employed).\n\n### **Step-by-Step Process**\n1. **Queueing:** Get a queue number and checklist of requirements.\n2. **Submission:** Submit the accomplished APL form and requirements to the Client Service Officer (CSO) for evaluation.\n3. **Application Payment:** Proceed to the Cashier and pay the **Application Fee (PHP 100)**.\n4. **Biometrics:** Proceed to the CSO window for the capturing of fingerprints, photo, and signature.\n5. **License Payment:** Pay the **License Fee (PHP 685)** at the Cashier.\n6. **Issuance:** Return to the Evaluator window to receive the printed Driver's License card. You will need to verify your identity via fingerprint scan and sign the log sheet.\n\n### **Fees and Time**\n- **Total Fee:** PHP 785 (PHP 100 Application Fee + PHP 685 License Fee).\n- **Total Processing Time:** Approximately 2 hours and 37 minutes.",
  "sources": [
    "DL-CC-2025.pdf"
